<item>
            <title>[LU-6356] Kerberos revival</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6356</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In current master branch, Kerberos support is not functional. Apart from issue described in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3778&quot; title=&quot;GSS doesn&amp;#39;t know about proxy subsystems&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3778&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3778&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, a number of areas in the code need to be fixed. The aim of this ticket is to gather information about the patches I made to revive Kerberos support in Lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sebastien.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
