&lt;p&gt;Question: Isn&apos;t the test still expected to fail when using a combined mgs+mds setup? tgt_connect_check_sptlrpc() has a &quot;== LOLND&quot; check, and if the check is successful the function authorizes usage of any flavour, so the test should not see the expected mds mount failure.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
